quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  29,1,‘ELIF-LAM-MIM
  29,2,‘EHESIBE EN-NASU ‘EN JUTREKU ‘EN JEKULU ‘AMENNA WE HUM LA JUFTENUNE
  29,3,WE LEKAD FETENNAL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM FELEJA’LEMENNEL-LAHUL-LEDHINE SEDEKU WE LEJA’LEMENNEL-KADHIBINE
  29,4,‘EM HESIBEL-LEDHINE JA’MELUNE ES-SEJJI’ATI ‘EN JESBIKUNA SA’E MA JEHKUMUNE
  29,5,MEN KANE JERXHU LIKA’EL-LAHI FE’INNE ‘EXHELEL-LAHI LE’ATIN WE HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-’ALIMU
  29,6,WE MEN XHAHEDE FE’INNEMA JUXHAHIDU LINEFSIHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE LEGANIJUN ‘ANIL-’ALEMINE
  29,7,WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI LENUKEFFIRENNE ‘ANHUM SEJJI’ATIHIM WE LENEXHZIJENNEHUM ‘EHSENEL-LEDHI KANU JA’MELUNE
  29,8,WE WESSEJNAL-’INSANE BIWALIDEJHI HUSNÆN WE ‘IN XHAHEDAKE LITUSHRIKE BI MA LEJSE LEKE BIHI ‘ILMUN FELA TUTI’HUMA ‘ILEJJE MERXHI’UKUM FE’UNEBBI’UKUM BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  29,9,WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI LENUDHILENNEHUM FI ES-SALIHINE
  29,10,WE MINE EN-NASI MEN JEKULU ‘AMENNA BILLAHI FE’IDHA ‘UDHIJE FI ELLAHI XHE’ALE FITNETE EN-NASI KE’ADHABI ELLAHI WE LE’IN XHA’E NESRUN MIN RABBIKE LEJEKULUNNE ‘INNA KUNNA ME’AKUM ‘EWELEJSEL-LAHU BI’A’LEME BIMA FI SUDURIL-’ALEMINE
  29,11,WE LEJA’LEMENNEL-LAHUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE LEJA’LEMENNEL-MUNAFIKINE
  29,12,WE KALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LILLEDHINE ‘AMENU ETTEBI’U SEBILENA WE LNEHMIL HATAJAKUM WE MA HUM BIHAMILINE MIN HATAJAHUM MIN SHEJ’IN ‘INNEHUM LEKADHIBUNE
  29,13,WE LEJEHMILUNNE ‘ETHKALEHUM WE ‘ETHKALÆN ME’A ‘ETHKALIHIM WE LEJUS’ELUNNE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘AMMA KANU JEFTERUNE